      "paragraphs": [
        "In some cultures, physical touch plays a significant role in farewells.  Think of the warm embrace common in many Latin American countries, or the traditional 'la bise' in France, where people lightly kiss each other's cheeks.  These gestures convey a sense of closeness and affection, emphasizing the importance of personal connection.",
